Stage 1 load-shedding will be in effect from 9am to 12 noon with stage 2 taking over until 11pm. JOHANNESBURG - Eskom will be implementing stage 1 and stage 2 loading-shedding on Friday Stage 1 load-shedding will be in effect from 9am to 12 noon with stage 2 taking over until 11pm. Eskom says they have suffered another setback as they have lost additional capacity from Medupi power station. The power utility says coal and ash handling issues are at the source of the problems today. 